    - "multiprocessing.managers.BaseProxy.__bases__[0].__name__ == 'object'. BaseProxy directly subclasses object. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.managers.BaseProxy.__mro__.__len__() == 2. MRO is [BaseProxy, object]. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.managers.BaseManager.__name__ == 'BaseManager'. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.managers.SyncManager.__name__ == 'SyncManager'. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
